{"tid":1450611,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T18:08:12.000Z","uid":153324,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6c8b684c51199455857d40fc80d3921a0231efa1","tid":1450611,"uid":153324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:45:27.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=c1735f05\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=bqZDxu8XrC4QaJB2Smgqvtey%2FoW3U1ZMpR7BmJTbZh4%3D&h=1a48b248\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"3f68730438958c022fb9324347979f3771026ae0","tid":1450611,"uid":153324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQmj4bJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQmj4bJ.jpg&h=d8b72b99&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c22d87a3437642f6c492f39f1a7063880d95604","tid":1450611,"uid":153324,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:46:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SaXrKbQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSaXrKbQ.jpg&h=cccb38a8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6778cbca190c6d5288e8811d56469